---
---
<section class="reveal py-[52.8px] bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-[1340px] w-full mx-auto px-[10px]">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-nav text-[19.2px] font-semibold tracking-[2.5px] text-[#A6587C] uppercase mb-3">FABRICS</h2>
      <h3 class="font-heading text-[52.8px] font-semibold leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mb-4">Excellent Material</h3>
      <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#757575] max-w-3xl mx-auto">We use a selection of high-performance fabrics specifically designed to enhance your athletic performance and comfort. Whether you’re a professional athlete or an enthusiastic fitness enthusiast, we have the fabrics you need to excel in your chosen sport.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href="/fabrics/" class="block group bg-[#F2F2F2] border border-[#A6587C] p-4">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[10px]">
          <img src="/images/fabrics/sitip-technical-textles-fabrics-1.webp" alt="Sitip Fabric" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105" />
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1D2F40] w-[80%] -mt-16 ml-auto mr-auto p-5 relative z-10 min-h-[220px]">
          <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4] mb-3">Sitip Italy Fabric – Premium European Quality</h4>
          <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#D9D9D9] mb-4">ICM uses Sitip fabrics made in Italy, delivering durability, structural stability, superior comfort, and high athletic performance.</p>
          <span class="font-nav text-[14.4px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-[#A6587C]">VIEW MORE</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/fabrics/" class="block group bg-[#F2F2F2] border border-[#A6587C] p-4">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[10px]">
          <img src="/images/fabrics/sitip-technical-textles-fabrics-2.webp" alt="Lightweight Fabric" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105" />
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1D2F40] w-[80%] -mt-16 ml-auto mr-auto p-5 relative z-10 min-h-[220px]">
          <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4] mb-3">Lightweight – Breathable – Quick-Dry</h4>
          <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#D9D9D9] mb-4">Sitip’s advanced textiles offer excellent breathability, fast-dry capability, and reliable stretch, ideal for training and competition.</p>
          <span class="font-nav text-[14.4px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-[#A6587C]">VIEW MORE</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/fabrics/" class="block group bg-[#F2F2F2] border border-[#A6587C] p-4">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[10px]">
          <img src="/images/fabrics/sitip-technical-textles-fabrics-3.webp" alt="Certifications" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105" />
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1D2F40] w-[80%] -mt-16 ml-auto mr-auto p-5 relative z-10 min-h-[220px]">
          <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4] mb-3">OEKO-TEX® – Bluesign® – GRS Certified</h4>
          <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#D9D9D9] mb-4">Sitip fabrics meet OEKO-TEX®, Bluesign®, and GRS standards for safety, sustainability, and environmental responsibility.</p>
          <span class="font-nav text-[14.4px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-[#A6587C]">VIEW MORE</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
